iguration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Sometimes it is necessary to limit a live video frame detection or recognition to a certain rectangular area with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a specific aspect ratio: the region or rectangle of interest. This is where a view finder comes in.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It crops the video frame to that region of interest before passing it to any scanner. Usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the performance of scanners gain a benefit from it because less pixels must be processed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Additionally, to guide the user, the view finder visualizes the region of interest by drawing a rectangle around","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the user interface.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerviewfinderconfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","type":"topic","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.4","type":"text"}]}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","op":"replace","value":"occ"},{"path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","op":"replace","value":"Instance Property"},{"path":"\/metadata\/title","op":"replace","value":"backgroundColor"},{"path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","op":"replace","value":"property"},{"path":"\/metadata\/fragments","op":"replace","value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"bac